title: chore(deps-dev): bump webpack-dev-server from 2.11.5 to 3.9.0 in /packages/xgplayer-flv
bodyText:
Bumps webpack-dev-server from 2.11.5 to 3.9.0.

Features

add multiple openPage support (#2266) (c9e9178)

v3.8.2
3.8.2 (2019-10-02)
Security

update selfsigned package

v3.8.1

Bug Fixes

add null check for connection.headers (#2200) (7964997)

scriptHost in client (#2246) (00903f6)

v3.8.0
3.8.0 (2019-08-09)
Bug Fixes
